---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About NoticePointBD" description="Learn about NoticePointBD and how we publish updates.">
  <article class="mx-auto my-8 max-w-3xl rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">About NoticePointBD</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      NoticePointBD is a static information portal focused on Bangladesh job circulars, admission notices, exam results, and helpful guides.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      Our goal is to publish clear and updated notices in a simple format so users can quickly understand application deadlines, eligibility basics, and source links.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      We do not process job applications directly. Users should always verify details from official circulars and websites before applying.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
